node.text: Thank you Jay for giving me the honor of kickstarting your “Think Like a Monk” book launch day. I’ve turned into a student again since reading it, taking notes and highlighting so many quotes to remember. I’m so grateful for our friendship and for all the inspiration you’ve given me in living my purpose and passion. Can’t wait for everyone to master your monk mindset. What a game changer!...

node.text: I'm so excited to finally be able to talk about a film that I had the privilege of making a few months ago with @charliemcdowell #JasonSegel and #JessePlemmons. I've never been part of something so intimate, collaborative and freeing. This brilliant script by @justinlader and @andykevinwalker provided me the opportunity to take ownership over a completely different character than any I've ever played before. Windfall was imagined, created, and finished during quarantine and I couldn't be prouder of our incredible crew for all the countless hours of hard work, safety and determination to make this labor of love a reality. Thank you @netflix for believing in our very outside-the-box film. It was a beautiful experience that turned into an incredible, bizarre piece of art and I can't wait for you all to see…

node.text: Happy birthday to the only man I know who makes breaking all the rules look so effortless. You never fail to add louder laughter to each moment we’re together, extra passion to everything you work on, double the adventure to any trip we take, and a greater love and support than I’ve ever felt before. You make my life brighter, safer, more centered and far more complete than I ever thought possible. I love you @charliemcdowell. I respect the artist you are and I adore the human you always have been. You make me a better person just by being around you. Plus, you’re hot. I can’t wait to be your wifey…
